headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Dewbauchee JB 700W
content: Just when you thought old school cool couldn’t get any cooler, the Dewbauchee JB 700W is back. And yes. This time, it’s weaponized. So don your tuxedo and spark the ignition with a wink and a witticism that’s aged like milk. If anyone complains, you know what to do.
